additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: Intentional misuse by deliberately concentrating and inhaling contents can be harmful or fatal. Keep out of reach of children and pets. Extremely flammable. Pressurised dispenser. Do not pierce or burn even after use. Protect from sunlight and avoid prolonged exposure to temperatures above 50C, such as may occur in cars, or near heat sources such as heaters, stove or open flame. Do not store, install or use near naked flame, heat or any incandescent material, for example near stoves, heaters, refrigerators. Do not smoke during use. Use only as directed.

description: Up to 60 days fragrance (Based on usage at low setting, 32 minute intervals).
name: Essential Oils Frangipani Refill
